msgstr ""

#: includes/privacy/class-privacy-tools.php
msgid "Donation records may be retained for the period configured by the site administrator (for accounting and tax-reporting purposes) and are anonymised or removed after that period. You can request export or erasure of your personal data using this site's privacy tools."
msgstr ""

